title: Champion Zeratul?
body: I must be tripping balls but when i went to check my top played champions in rank, it showed on my top 5 a champion called "Zeratul". I was thinking 'wtf'. The picture of it was a question mark on it. It's probably a bug but i saw the actual name "Zeratul". If this is a new champion thats pretty awesome but I honestly doubt that. Did anyone else experience this? Or is it just me?

replies.body: m8 you were playing star craft and that's why it also said wood 5
